OL,3,CPeople face #80 fine for leaving
OL,4,Cwheelie bins on road with warning
OL,5,Cletters sent
OL,7,FA council has sent out more than 100
OL,8,Fwarning letters to some of its
OL,9,Fresidents in efforts to keep public
OL,10,Fpavements free of wheelie bins.
OL,12,FPeople living in Southend face an #80
OL,13,Ffine if they are found to be
OL,14,Fcontinually leaving their refuse and
OL,15,Frecycling bins, empty-or-not, outside
OL,16,Ftheir property.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
