OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772615079
OL,3,CPeople face #80 fine for leaving
OL,4,Cwheelie bins on road with warning
OL,5,Cletters sent
OL,7,FMeanwhile, people who continually
OL,8,Fleave bin liners full of rubbish
OL,9,Foutside the boundary of their home
OL,10,Fcould be given a #1,000 under fly-
OL,11,Ftipping rules.
OL,13,FThe enforcement and education approach
OL,14,Fis being taken because the city
OL,15,Fcouncil says bins being left on the
OL,16,Fwrong side of a property's boundary
OL,17,Fare obstructing wheelchair users,
OL,18,Fparents with pushchairs and people who
OL,19,Fare visually impaired.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
