PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772615079
OL,3,CPeople face #80 fine for leaving
OL,4,Cwheelie bins on road with warning
OL,5,Cletters sent
OL,7,FSo far, 135 educational letters have
OL,8,Fbeen issued to residents where bins
OL,9,Fwere not being stored correctly.
OL,11,FIf people repeatedly refuse to comply
OL,12,Fthen a fixed penalty notice may be
OL,13,Fissued as a last resort, but fines
OL,14,Fwill not be given to people who don't
OL,15,Fbring their bins in on collection day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
