FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772615079
OL,3,CPeople face #80 fine for leaving
OL,4,Cwheelie bins on road with warning
OL,5,Cletters sent
OL,7,FCouncillor Lydia Hyde, Cabinet Member
OL,8,Ffor Climate, Environment and Waste,
OL,9,Fsaid, "We have written to a small
OL,10,Fnumber of residents across Southend to
OL,11,Fencourage them to bring their bins
OL,12,Fback onto their property.
OL,14,F"This first letter is educational and
OL,15,Fsets out the consequences of not doing
OL,16,Fso, which may include an #80 fixed
OL,17,Fpenalty notice. However, if residents
OL,18,Fbring their bins in as requested, no
OL,19,Ffurther action will be taken.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
