PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772615079
OL,3,CPeople face #80 fine for leaving
OL,4,Cwheelie bins on road with warning
OL,5,Cletters sent
OL,7,FOn social media, Councillor Hyde
OL,8,Fadded, "The overwhelming majority of
OL,9,Fresidents will never receive a fine.
OL,11,F"However, we are taking stronger
OL,12,Faction against the small minority who
OL,13,Frepeatedly obstruct pavements or
OL,14,Fcreate persistent waste problems that
OL,15,Faffect their neighbours and the
OL,16,Fcleanliness of our city."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
